reviewText: Classic RVL! If you were blessed by volumes 1-14, you are going to love this one too.
This captures a sense of being there.
As always, all programs in this series are first-class and great teaching tools
I love his series, but on this DVD the 4th lesson seems to be a "repeat" of the first one on this DVD???
Excellent material and video production. Well worth buying. Great product. I recommend ALL of Ray's videos!
Ray has lived up to his outstanding reputation. I always learn a LOT with his teachings
RVL produces a quality educational DVD series.  Try it -- you'll like it!
